      </p>

     </div>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA06d184n1-ptr" id="PJA06d184n1">1</a>
      
   <p>Not found.</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA06d184n2-ptr" id="PJA06d184n2">2</a>
      
   <p>See Benjamin Franklin and <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> to American State Officials, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-06-02-0098" class="document">18 May</a> (calendared above).</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA06d184n3-ptr" id="PJA06d184n3">3</a>
      
   <p>For further information on the sailing of the fleet, as well as James Beams, who is mentioned in the last paragraph, see Coffyns letter of <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-06-02-0162" class="document">19 June</a> (below).</p>

